blog.name: pod-together
blog.title: Pod Together
blog.description:
Welcome to pod_together, a challenge where writers and podficcers create together—the writer writing something specifically to be podficced, and the podficcer recording it.
Rules, FAQ, and sign-ups are on our dreamwidth.  Works created from previous years of this challenge can be found in our AO3 collection. Banner and promos by reena_jenkins.

summary:
MCU writers and podficcers, if you’re interested in a collaborative
challenge, we’d love to have you as part of this year’s...
caption:
MCU writers and podficcers, if you’re interested in a collaborative challenge, we’d love to have you as part of this year’s pod_together!

pod_together is a multifandom, multimedia challenge that pairs writers and podficcers to create a collaborative fanwork - the writer writing something specifically intended for audio, and the podficcer creating the audio version.

Are you a writer or podficcer who wants to try something experimental in a supportive environment while making a new friend? Sign up as an individual, and we’ll find you a partner with compatible fandoms and interests to create with! Are you worried about being matched to someone you don’t know? Grab a friend and sign up as a group! Create your new work together!

If you’d like to check out past pod_together works, you can find them here. The Rules/FAQ for the challenge are here. Sign-ups are open until June 8th. We’d love to see you there!

summary: Road Trip With Carol Danvers Headcanons: she likes to drive for the most part  will let you drive it she gets tired but that...
body:
Road Trip With Carol Danvers Headcanons:

  • she likes to drive for the most part
  • will let you drive it she gets tired
  • but that hardly ever happens because she has so much energy 
  • loves to listen to early 90′s tunes 
  • windows down all the time so the cool air can whip through your hair 
  • adores driving fast so the trip is never as long as you expect 
  • holding your hand while she drives 
  • wears her leather jacket and aviator sunglasses 
  • loves to play I spy 
  • “I spy something beautiful,” she grins looking over at you
  • will race people if any opportunity presents itself
  • always brings loads of snacks 
  • Carol also brings along a Polaroid camera so she can snap some pictures along the way 
  • so much singing along to the music 
  • Carol always sings loud and proud  
  • she knows every song 
  • drapes her jacket over you when you fall asleep 
  • makes sure to turn the music down whenever your eyes close
  •  also does her best to avoid the potholes while you rest 
  • her car always smells like mahogany and amber
